title: Return of officer
context: [§654-6] Return of officer. The officer shall return the order on or before the return day specified in the order issued to the officer and state fully what the officer has done thereunder. If the officer has taken any property the officer shall describe the same particularly. [L Sp 1949, c 7, pt of §1; RL 1955, §244-26; HRS §654-27; ren HRS §654-6; gen ch 1985]
